Text: Belatedbirthday Kevin just asked me if I knew it was your birthday yesterday I completely forgot you were celebrating your th I hope you had a great one me
are you aroundi just tried calling you but i guess someone hung up on me call me when you get a chance

MarisaI just wanted to forward this information to you just in case you have not received it Could you please forward the info to Eric Sturm and anyone else who you think might want to attend I hope all is well Jemmina Original Message From Nagle Rita mailto Sent Tuesday October AM To Gualy Jemmina Subject Marisa A memorial service has been planned for Marisa on Oct It will be held at St Anthonys Church in West Harrison NY I can get directions to the church if you think anyone in Houston would want them I plan on attending and am happy to house youothers that will be in the area Please spread the word to anyone who you think should know I dont know many of her trading friendsand let me know if you are planning on coming I am here to help any way possible Take good care Rita
